data.description: The Home is virtually staged.    Discover Luxury living in this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath condo nestled in the heart of Hampton. A Gated Community. This exquisite home offers a seamless blend of comfort and sophistication, featuring a freshly painted interior. Vaulted ceilings and skylights give a bright, spacious  airy feel to this home. The Kitchen has stainless appliances and granite countertops where you can delight in preparing meals. Enjoy breathtaking views of the lake from your private patio, an ideal retreat for relaxation or entertaining.This community has marina access and offers the unique opportunity for boat storage, great for water enthusiasts. Amenities include clubhouse, gym, tennis courts & community boat slips.  Water is covered in the association fee. This Condo is not just a home it"s a lifestyle. Located near interstate 64, malls, shops & entertainment.  ***** Seller to provide 12 months paid condo and association fees with acceptable offer.*****
